Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&D5DDE0}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}他好像找到伯斯哈夫特了
