Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\c&F1F1F0\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}是八十年 法斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\c&F1F1F0\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}80年ぶりだよ ファス
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur0.7\c&F1F1F0\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}怕不是我认错人了
