Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}是旅费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}路銀です
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\blur0.7\3c&333333\4c&333333}称得上巨款了
