Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&95A7C4}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&13141A\4c&13141A}这活儿我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&95A7C4}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&13141A\4c&13141A}お受けします
